*Uses task_create to create: "Fix type errors"*

*Uses task_update to mark "Run the build" as in_progress*
Running the build now...

Found 10 type errors. Let me create subtasks for each.
*Uses task_create with parentTaskId to create subtasks for each error*

*Uses task_update to mark the first error fix as in_progress*
Working on the first error...

*Uses task_update to mark the first error as completed, moves to the next*
..
